description: Kellogg's Frosted Flakes, Breakfast Cereal, Honey Nut, Made With Real Honey, 13.7oz Box

Start your day off right with Tony the Tiger and Kellogg's honey Nut frosted Flakes—a delicious cereal that helps you let your gr-r-reat out with every crunchy spoonful. Sweetened to perfection, with the delicious taste of honey for a breakfast that will get you buzzing for the day. Each satisfying serving contains an excellent source of 7 vitamins and minerals to help energize your morning. Not just for BREAKFAST, Kellogg's honey Nut Frosted Flakes is a tasty and nutritious addition to any meal or snack any time of the day. Enjoy as a snack at the office, take in an afternoon pick-me-up, reenergize with a post-workout treat, and indulge in a late-night bowlful of sweet, crunchy cereal. Kellogg's honey Nut Frosted Flakes also makes a great addition to your favorite yogurt or as the base for a fun homemade trail mix—the mouthwatering options are endless. A travel-ready food, Kellogg's Frosted Flakes is an ideal companion for lunchboxes and busy, on-the-go moments. Just add your favorite dairy or plant-based milk or enjoy as a crispy treat straight from the box.
